      Feedback from designers, developers, and managers I've worked with at enterprise clients.
    </p>
  </SectionIntro>
  <div class="testimonial-grid">
    <!-- Populated with LinkedIn recommendations — Tom to provide quotes before launch -->
    <TestimonialCard
      quote="Placeholder — Tom to replace with real LinkedIn recommendation before launch."
      name="Colleague Name"
      title="Role, Company"
    />
